# Cloud Policy as Code DSL Compiler — Steps 1 & 2

Complete the first two phases of the compiler: designing the formal DSL grammar and implementing the lexer (tokenizer) using Flex. This gives us the language definition and character-level scanning layer that all subsequent stages depend on.

---

